Company Overview of Atlantic Trust Company, N.A.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Atlantic Trust Company, N.A., a private wealth management company, provides integrated wealth management services for high net worth individuals, families, foundations, and endowments. The company considers clients’ financial, trust, estate planning, and philanthropic needs in developing customized asset allocation and investment management solutions. It offers investment management services, including investment selection, internal strategies, manager access, and alternative investment; and wealth advisory services, including fiduciary, stable, flexible trustee, planning resource, family advisor, and philanthropic legacy. The company was founded in 1923 and is based in Boston, Massachusetts...
Atlantic Trust Company, N.A., a private wealth management company, provides integrated wealth management services for high net worth individuals, families, foundations, and endowments. The company considers clients’ financial, trust, estate planning, and philanthropic needs in developing customized asset allocation and investment management solutions. It offers investment management services, including investment selection, internal strategies, manager access, and alternative investment; and wealth advisory services, including fiduciary, stable, flexible trustee, planning resource, family advisor, and philanthropic legacy. The company was founded in 1923 and is based in Boston, Massachusetts with locations in Atlanta, Austin, Baltimore, Boston, Chicago, Denver, Houston, New York, Newport Beach, San Francisco, Washington, and Wilmington. It also has offices in West Palm Beach, Florida; and Austin, Houston, and Dallas, Texas. Atlantic Trust Company, N.A. operates as a subsidiary of Atlantic Trust Group, LLC.
